# Curly Braces For Conditionals

- Always wrap `if` statement bodies in curly braces, even for single-line returns or simple statements.
- Do not use single-line `if` statements without braces.
- Keep the statement body indented inside the block.

```typescript
// Bad
if (condition) return value;

// Good
if (condition) {
  return value;
}
```
